{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/test/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"F&Y-BLOG","author":"kimifdw"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8f8722d3-ad18-5212-a0ea-9495a33d55c3","html":"<h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>定义</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>测试在先，编码灾后，采用“红-绿-重构”三个步骤的循环往复。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>红：测试先行，现在还没有任何实现，跑 UT 的时候肯定不过，测试状态是红灯。编译失败也属于“红”的一种情况。</li>\n<li>绿：当我们用最快，最简单的方式先实现，然后跑一遍 UT，测试会通过，变成“绿”的状态。</li>\n<li>重构：看一下系统中有没有要重构的点，重构完，一定要保证测试是“绿”的。</li>\n<li>TDD 比较适合用于输入输出很明确的 CASE</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"特性\"><a href=\"#%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>特性</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>隔离性。单元测试之间应该隔离，不要互相干扰</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"资料\"><a href=\"#%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>资料</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://martinfowler.com/articles/practical-test-pyramid.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">practical-test-pyramid</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://insights.thoughtworks.cn/practical-test-pyramid/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">中文翻译</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/TjJ31yWTMwr4szz1JqtKcQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">测试资料</a></li>\n</ol>","timeToRead":1,"frontmatter":{"title":"测试驱动","date":"November 02, 2020","spoiler":"TDD"},"fields":{"slug":"/test/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/test/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/spring-boot/","directoryName":"spring-boot"},"frontmatter":{"title":"spring boot部分源码解读"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/netty-memory/","directoryName":"netty-memory"},"frontmatter":{"title":"netty内存原理"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["336482444"]}